headline.main: Christopher Bell Finishes Off Dominant Truck Win at Atlanta
headline.print_headline: Christopher Bell Finishes Off Dominant Truck Win at Atlanta

lead_paragraph: Nick Rimando made three saves for Real Salt Lake, including two against Sebastian Giovinco, to help Real Salt Lake tie defending Eastern Conference champion Toronto FC 0-0 on Saturday in a Major League Soccer opener.
